player.signature: 呪物揃ったのでアスター最強厨になります

skills.name: Spectrum Beam
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Fire DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Fire DMG equal to 60% of Asta's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Meteor Storm
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Fire DMG to single enemy targets with 5 Bounces in total.
skills.desc: Deals Fire DMG equal to 43% of Asta's ATK to a single enemy and further deals DMG for 4 extra times, with each time dealing Fire DMG equal to 43% of Asta's ATK to a random enemy.

skills.name: Astral Blessing
skills.desc: Increases SPD of all allies by 43 for 2 turn(s).

skills.name: Astrometry
skills.simple_desc: The character will receive 1 stack of Charging for every different enemy they hit, for a maximum of 5 stacks. Every stack of Charging increases ATK for all allies. At the beginning of their turn, reduce Charging stacks.
skills.desc:
Gains 1 stack of Charging for every different enemy hit by Asta plus an extra stack if the enemy hit has Fire Weakness.
For every stack of Charging Asta has, all allies' ATK increases by 11.4%, up to 5 time(s).
Starting from her second turn, Asta's Charging stack count is reduced by 3 at the beginning of every turn.

skills.name: Miracle Flash
skills.simple_desc: Attacks the enemy. After entering battle, deals minor amounts of DMG to all enemies.
skills.desc: Immediately attacks the enemy. After entering battle, deals Fire DMG equal to 50% of Asta's ATK to all enemies.

relic_sets.name: Thief of Shooting Meteor
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's Break Effect by 16%. When the wearer inflicts Weakness Break on an enemy, regenerates 3 Energy.

relic_sets.name: Inert Salsotto
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's CRIT Rate by 8%. When the wearer's current CRIT Rate reaches 50% or higher, the wearer's Ultimate and follow-up attack DMG increases by 15%.

skills.name: I Want to Help
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Physical DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Physical DMG equal to 80% of Clara's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Svarog Watches Over You
skills.simple_desc: Deals Physical DMG to all enemies. Additionally deals Physical DMG to targets with Marks of Counter.
skills.desc:
Deals Physical DMG equal to 105% of Clara's ATK to all enemies, and additionally deals Physical DMG equal to 105% of Clara's ATK to enemies marked by Svarog with a Mark of Counter.
All Marks of Counter will be removed after this Skill is used.

skills.name: Promise, Not Command
skills.simple_desc: Reduces DMG received, increases chance to be attacked by enemies, and enhances Counters.
skills.desc:
After Clara uses Ultimate, DMG dealt to her is reduced by an extra 22%, and she has greatly increased chances of being attacked by enemies for 2 turn(s).
In addition, Svarog's Counter is enhanced. When an ally is attacked, Svarog immediately launches a Counter, and its DMG multiplier against the enemy increases by 144%. Enemies adjacent to it take 50% of the DMG dealt to the target enemy. Enhanced Counter(s) can take effect 2 time(s).

skills.name: Because We're Family
skills.simple_desc: DMG received from enemy attacks is reduced. Enemies who attack Clara will be marked with a Mark of Counter and met with Svarog's Counter, dealing Physical DMG.
skills.desc: Under the protection of Svarog, DMG taken by Clara when hit by enemy attacks is reduced by 10%. Svarog will mark enemies who attack Clara with his Mark of Counter and retaliate with a Counter, dealing Physical DMG equal to 150% of Clara's ATK.

skills.name: A Small Price for Victory
skills.simple_desc: Attacks the enemy. After entering battle, this character's chance of being attacked by enemies increases.
skills.desc: Immediately attacks the enemy. Upon entering battle, the chance Clara will be attacked by enemies increases for 2 turn(s).

relic_sets.name: Champion of Streetwise Boxing
relic_sets.desc: After the wearer attacks or is hit, their ATK increases by 5% for the rest of the battle. This effect can stack up to 5 time(s).

relic_sets.name: Inert Salsotto
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's CRIT Rate by 8%. When the wearer's current CRIT Rate reaches 50% or higher, the wearer's Ultimate and follow-up attack DMG increases by 15%.

skills.name: Thwack
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Quantum DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Quantum DMG equal to 80% of Seele's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Sheathed Blade
skills.simple_desc: Deals Quantum DMG to a single enemy and increases SPD.
skills.desc: Increases Seele's SPD by 25% for 2 turn(s) and deals Quantum DMG equal to 192% of Seele's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Butterfly Flurry
skills.simple_desc: Enters the buffed state and deals massive Quantum DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Seele enters the buffed state and deals Quantum DMG equal to 340% of her ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Resurgence
skills.desc:
Enters the buffed state upon defeating an enemy with Basic ATK, Skill, or Ultimate, and receives an extra turn. While in the buffed state, the DMG of Seele's attacks increases by 60% for 1 turn(s).
Enemies defeated in the extra turn provided by "Resurgence" will not trigger another "Resurgence."

skills.name: Phantom Illusion
skills.desc: After using her Technique, Seele gains Stealth for 20 second(s). While Stealth is active, Seele cannot be detected by enemies. And when entering battle by attacking enemies, Seele will immediately enter the buffed state.

relic_sets.name: Genius of Brilliant Stars
relic_sets.desc: When the wearer deals DMG to the target enemy, ignores 10% DEF. If the target enemy has Quantum Weakness, the wearer additionally ignores 10% DEF.

relic_sets.name: Inert Salsotto
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's CRIT Rate by 8%. When the wearer's current CRIT Rate reaches 50% or higher, the wearer's Ultimate and follow-up attack DMG increases by 15%.
